          <td class="item-description">
            <h2><i>Witness the Wackness</i></h2>
            <p>
<i>Witness the Wackness</i> is a CD of my own music, produced in limited numbers and intended as an experiment in incorporating illustration into packaging design.
<br></br>
I wanted to create a piece of illustrative work which could be handled and touched, so I used bright colours and distinctive textures, including felt, and several card and paper stocks, to make the process of opening the packaging into a surprising, exploratory experience, like opening a carefully wrapped present.
<br></br>
I incorporated a wide range of illustrative approaches into the piece, creating a combination of photographed and hand-drawn elements for the packaging and an abstract design inspired by textile designs by Maija Isola for the disc.
            </p>
          </td>
